 ('2', '2', 'en_us', 'About Kent Student Media', '<p>Award-winning, nationally recognized and locally focused. Our independent, student-run media partners create content the campus and Kent community seek. Students learn practical skills through the professional learning opportunities available through Kent State Student Media. Advertising with Kent State Student Media is an excellent way to make sure you reach your audience.</p>', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'This is our description', NULL, 'Tigger the dog', 'Kent State Student Media is made by students, for students.', NULL, NULL, '', 'https://player.vimeo.com/video/183532877', NULL, '0', NULL, NULL, '2017-01-12 16:12:59', '2017-03-16 20:46:20', 'f78f163d-6654-40b7-9f92-e347dd1a8a48'),
 ('3', '3', 'en_us', 'We just installed Craft!', '<p>Craft is the CMS that’s powering Kentstatestudentmedia.com. It’s beautiful, powerful, flexible, and easy-to-use, and it’s made by Pixel &amp; Tonic. We can’t wait to dive in and see what it’s capable of!</p><!--pagebreak--><p>This is even more captivating content, which you couldn’t see on the News index page because it was entered after a Page Break, and the News index template only likes to show the content on the first page.</p><p>Craft: a nice alternative to Word, if you’re making a website.</p>', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '0', NULL, NULL, '2017-01-12 16:12:59', '2017-01-12 16:12:59', 'dfa73501-ee0c-49a1-9e07-9d9311da2157'),
