 ('10', '10', 'en_us', 'A Magazine', NULL, NULL, '', '[]', '', '', NULL, NULL, '', 'A Magazine is a visually stunning student-run magazine at Kent State. It is the publication for all things fashion, beauty, accessories and culture on campus and beyond. A focuses on both women\'s and men\'s fashion and has companion website that is updated regularly with extended content and videos, providing students with the latest fashion news. It is distributed at Kent State and the Fashion School’s New York studio.', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'A Magazine is Kent State’s student-run fashion magazine and is the hub for all things fashion, beauty and culture related.', '1', NULL, NULL, '2017-02-23 21:56:29', '2017-03-16 19:28:02', '6f8e97bf-9f33-417d-ac37-a04cb04c79ba'),
 ('11', '11', 'en_us', '105', NULL, NULL, NULL, '[]', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'This is a description of the statistic', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'Publications', NULL, NULL, '0', NULL, NULL, '2017-02-24 21:50:46', '2017-03-16 20:44:04', 'b37eef99-19a3-4fa9-9c81-deed5db3e4e2'),
 ('12', '12', 'en_us', '750', NULL, NULL, NULL, '[]', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'This is a description of the second statistic', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'Students work with student media per semester', NULL, NULL, '0', NULL, NULL, '2017-02-24 21:51:00', '2017-03-16 20:43:37', '7fc4b890-5442-4999-84b0-b9bf626cf39f'),
 ('14', '14', 'en_us', 'The Burr', NULL, NULL, '', '[]', '', '', NULL, NULL, '', 'The Burr is an independent, award-winning student magazine and was Kent State’s first student magazine ever. The magazine features a mix of original reporting, how-to articles, feature articles and personal essays. TheBurr.com is frequently updated with multimedia stories and blogs and has an archive of past issues.', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'The Burr is Kent State’s first student-produced magazine made for those who have made a home in Kent.', '1', NULL, NULL, '2017-02-27 15:21:05', '2017-03-16 19:26:26', '45cdefa8-367e-4d2d-9733-583b8f9829b4'),
 ('15', '15', 'en_us', 'Kent Stater', NULL, NULL, '', '[]', '', '', NULL, NULL, '', 'The Kent Stater is the award-winning, student-run newspaper at Kent State University. Reaching more than 15,000 people per issue, the Stater keeps the community up-to-date with campus, local and national news, sports and features. The Stater publishes on Monday, Wednesday and Thursday and has a circulation of 6,750 per day. During the summer months, The Kent Stater runs special print issues and also runs the annual Orientation issue to welcome new and returning students.', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'The Kent Stater is the award-winning, student-run newspaper at Kent State University. ', '1', NULL, NULL, '2017-02-27 15:21:14', '2017-03-16 19:27:28', '7e622988-7d52-4011-872c-1c063f8dcc6e'),
 ('19', '19', 'en_us', 'Black Squirrel Radio', NULL, NULL, '', '[]', '', '', NULL, NULL, '', 'Black Squirrel Radio (BSR) is a student-run radio station that has 10,000 loyal monthly listeners. BSR features a large selection of urban, rock and local music with numerous local bands and entertainers coming for in-studio performances and interviews. BSR is available at www.blacksquirrelradio.com, iTunes radio under College Stations, the TuneIn app and channels 2-4 and 2-6 though on-campus television.', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'Black Squirrel Radio (BSR) is the student-run radio station on Kent State’s campus and provides innovative media content inspired by the community of Kent, Ohio.', '1', NULL, NULL, '2017-03-02 19:46:01', '2017-03-16 19:11:04', 'b9058ae3-0353-4198-93c6-ca8357c03eb1'),
 ('20', '20', 'en_us', 'TV2', NULL, NULL, '', '[]', '', '', NULL, NULL, '', 'TV2 is the award-winning, student-run television station of Kent State University. TV2 is also Portage County’s only local television station and the best source for local news and original television content. TV2 reaches more than 26,000 homes throughout Portage County on Spectrum (formerly Time Warner Cable) channel 16 and more than 7,500 Kent State students living on-campus on channel 2-2. TV2 is also live streamed on KentWired.com/TV2. With 10 different TV shows, TV2 covers everything from breaking news, local news, weather, sports, entertainment and humor.', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'TV2 is the award-winning, student-run television station of Kent State that broadcasts to students and the Portage County community.', '1', NULL, NULL, '2017-03-02 19:46:26', '2017-03-23 17:55:20', 'a23b03af-0e18-4a7b-8901-95644568668e'),
 ('21', '21', 'en_us', 'Fusion Magazine', NULL, NULL, '', '[]', '', '', NULL, NULL, '', 'Fusion is Kent State\'s lesbian, gay, bisexual, transgender and queer/questioning student advocacy and entertainment magazine. Fusion strives to promote equality and community in northeast Ohio and beyond through journalism and they have been recognized by the Society of Professional Journalists for excellence. Fusion is the only student magazine focusing on LGBTQ issues in the region.', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'Fusion is Kent State\'s lesbian, gay, bisexual, transgender and queer/questioning student advocacy and entertainment magazine. ', '1', NULL, NULL, '2017-03-02 19:46:47', '2017-03-16 19:12:44', '7588d518-0261-46ab-a865-1600d104616c'),
 ('22', '22', 'en_us', 'Uhuru', NULL, NULL, '', '[]', '', '', NULL, NULL, '', 'Uhuru is an award-winning magazine that promotes innovation, creativity and culture through the voice of marginalized students. A derivative of Black Unites Students, Uhuru is focused on the unification of the African-American population but serves as a safe haven for others by reflecting all people of color at Kent State. Uhuru is Kent State\'s only minority news outlet and serves as a platform for student creation and expression in art, writing, photography and graphic design while addressing social issues.', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'Uhuru is the magazine that promotes innovation, creativity and culture through the voice of marginalized students at Kent State.', '1', NULL, NULL, '2017-03-02 19:46:53', '2017-03-16 19:13:21', 'b1238632-d5b9-44ea-a4f5-8584bb4f074e'),
 ('23', '23', 'en_us', 'KentWired', NULL, NULL, '', '[]', '', '', NULL, NULL, '', 'KentWired.com is a news organization hosting content created by the collaborative effort of students working in student media at Kent State University. KentWired is the independent news website for the Kent Stater and TV2 and is the year round news source for everything Kent. KentWired has top news, entertainment, sports, and community and campus news. It also features classifieds and live streams for TV2 and Black Squirrel Radio. ', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'KentWired.com is a news organization that holds content created by students working in student media at Kent State University. ', '1', NULL, NULL, '2017-03-02 19:48:46', '2017-03-16 20:33:51', 'ecc0b93e-3f1e-4938-9f03-c3892be4e7ac'),
 ('24', '24', 'en_us', 'Luna Negra', NULL, NULL, '', '[]', '', '', NULL, NULL, '', 'Luna Negra is Kent State’s literary student publication and they publish a blend of poetry, prose, photography and illustration. For over 50 years, they have published submissions from current students and community members. Their magazine is published every spring and they produce additional content on LunaNegraMag.com.', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'Luna Negra is Kent State’s literary student magazine that publishes a blend of poetry, prose, photography and illustration. ', '1', NULL, NULL, '2017-03-02 19:49:24', '2017-04-13 14:54:10', '64fa8053-5481-4595-9f99-d2f2720dbed5'),
 ('25', '25', 'en_us', 'KSU Independent Films', NULL, NULL, 'us@kent.edu', '[]', 'Rob', 'Flash', NULL, NULL, '330-672-6541', 'Kent State University Independent Films (KSUIF) is a student-run production company that teaches, inspires and prepares filmmakers for the real-world industry. KSUIF produces a wide variety of content including webseries, short films, award-winning music videos, documentaries, TV shows and feature films. KSUIF is one of three organizations in the country that allows students to create full-length feature films.', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'Kent State University Independent Films (KSUIF) is a student-run production company that teaches, inspires and prepares filmmakers for the real-world industry. ', '1', NULL, NULL, '2017-03-02 19:49:47', '2017-04-13 14:56:32', 'd408f63f-0d5c-42e8-84c9-70b90293d6dd'),
